item.description:
lets climb quincy quarries.  we'll meet in the parking lot if you get there before 10am if running late meet at J/K wall.  if you dont know were these walls are just ask someone. those that has ropes bring them also slings and webbing to set up top ropes. since this is a LRG group we'll most likely split up and hit up some other walls.

 

BRING: Sun Block, water, snacks, and anything else you feel you will need.

 

with the sun setting later now, we could be climbing into the early evening.
item.name: Climbing at Quincy Quarries
